## Part 3 - Platform Data Architecture

## Platform Data Philosophy

Different platform capabilities have different storage requirements.

Never force all data into relational tables.

Choose the appropriate storage model based on the nature of the data.

Business data belongs in PostgreSQL.

Large binary objects belong in S3.

Vector data belongs in pgvector.

Search projections belong in the Search Service.

